description: Special Agent Cox Smulder (Devin Franco) wants to prove he was abducted by an alien, but with a skeptic of a partner like Agent Sully (Damon Heart) it’s easy to get pulled back to earth. With one unsolved mystery after another, Sully and Smulder find themselves closer to the truth, until they come face to face -- and face to cock… and ass to mouth -- with a close encounter of the probing kind.
title: The XXX Files | Devin Franco, Damon Heart, Bogdan Gromov
